nodes.title: Caption Prompt
widgets_values: a muscular, bald, humanoid warrior with a fierce expression, standing in a desert-like environment with ancient Egyptian ruins in the background. He is wearing a purple cloth draped around his waist, a gold belt with a circular medallion, and orange armor with robotic features. He has a long antennae on his head, and his body is toned and muscular. The sky is clear and blue, with a few clouds scattered across it. The artwork is highly detailed and realistic, with vibrant colors and sharp lines. The warrior is the main subject, positioned in the center of the video.
